This product includes software developed by Kavara
(https://kavara.ai).

This reference implementation demonstrates the dispatch architecture used in
Kavara's production `ts_sor_base` package. The production package carries
additional numerical backends (C/MKL fused kernels, oneDNN AMX BRGEMM) and
model-specific physics primitives that are not redistributed here.

Policy table values (THRESHOLD_PROFILES, VENUE_POLICIES, BUCKET_THRESHOLDS)
in sor_router.py are derived from empirical calibration experiments conducted
by Kavara's platform engineering team on Intel Granite Rapids hardware inside
Intel TDX Trust Domains. See README.md for experiment provenance.
